5
00:00:15,054 --> 00:00:20,245
In this program, Juno will focus on programming tools specifically Python,

6
00:00:20,245 --> 00:00:24,265
one of the most widely used programming languages in the industry.

7
00:00:24,265 --> 00:00:29,815
Juan Delgado, a computational physicist with a Masters in Astronomy.

8
00:00:29,815 --> 00:00:31,760
