14
00:00:50,539 --> 00:00:54,839
the most mature Python package for data visualization.

15
00:00:54,840 --> 00:00:59,005
Jennifer Stab, holds a PhD in Computer Science,

16
00:00:59,005 --> 00:01:01,535
