29
00:01:54,474 --> 00:01:57,734
Mat Leonard, a former Physicist,

30
00:01:57,734 --> 00:02:01,079
Research Neuroscientist and Data scientist.

31
00:02:01,079 --> 00:02:03,709
He completed his PhD and Postdoctoral

32
00:02:03,709 --> 00:02:07,289
Fellowship at the University of California in Berkeley.

33
00:02:07,290 --> 00:02:12,730
You will see Mat throughout the program in various lessons such as Pytorch.

34
00:02:12,729 --> 00:02:18,318
